data.description: Welcome to your PERFECT haven! This STUNNING home not only features a light and bright open floor plan but also offers a thoughtful SPLIT floor plan, providing an ideal layout for both privacy and togetherness. As you explore the home, you'll be delighted by the SPACIOUS primary bedroom, a true retreat with its generous size and abundance of natural light. The primary bedroom comes with a slider door providing DIRECT access to the enchanting SALT WATER POOL, creating a seamless blend of indoor and outdoor living. Imagine waking up and stepping directly into your private paradise.   The second and third bedrooms, perfect for guests or family members, boast an en-suite bathroom in the second bedroom, ensuring both comfort and convenience. Additionally, this home features several upgrades including gutters with gutter guards installed in 2023, a New roof added in 2024, an exterior wood fence on both sides of the property with gates, a Refrigerator installed in 2023, a Dishwasher also added in 2023, a Water softener installed in 2021, HVAC upgraded in 2021, a metal shed (6x8) on a concrete pad, and a gas hook-up available. The knockdown smooth ceilings add a touch of sophistication to the living space.   The well-designed layout, coupled with the luxurious amenities, creates a harmonious living space that meets the needs of modern living. Whether you're entertaining by the pool, enjoying the privacy of your primary suite, or utilizing the convenient inside utility room, every aspect of this home has been carefully crafted for your comfort and enjoyment. This residence offers a perfect blend of functionality and elegance, making it the ideal place to call home. Don't miss the chance to experience the lifestyle you've been dreaming of – schedule your showing today!
